            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>The voice of Doraemon since 2005.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Wasabi Mizuta, the long-time voice of Doraemon since the 2005 television series, will voice Monokuma in <em><a title="Games > Danganronpa 2x2 [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/danganronpa-2x2">Danganronpa 2×2</a></em>, <a title="Companies > Spike Chunsoft [895 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/kadokawa-corporation/spike-chunsoft">Spike Chunsoft</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/dangan_official/status/1981560582563307707" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-1002340"></span></p><p>Monokuma is a key character in the <em><a title="Series > Danganronpa [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/danganronpa">Danganronpa</a></em> series. He was voiced by Nobuyo Oyama until 2016, who was similarly was the voice of Doraemon from 1979 to 2005, then by Tarako until her passing in 2024.</p><p>Alongside the announcement, Spike Chunsoft released a new video introducing Mizuta as Monokuma’s new voice actor.</p><p><em>Danganronpa 2×2</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,692 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,167 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [584 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,878 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,637 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3751230/Danganronpa_2x2/" target="_blank">Steam</a> in 2026.</p><p>Watch the video below.</p><h2><span>Greetings from Monokuma</span></h2><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><iframe title="『スーパーダンガンロンパ２×２』モノクマからのご挨拶！【Nintendo Switch 2 / Nintendo Switch / PS5 / Xbox Series X|S / Steam】" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LUlWICZP9XM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/danganronpa-2x2-monokuma-voiced-by-wasabi-mizuta]]></content:encoded>
